originalText.text: I had an awesome experience at Radiant Skin NYC with Dr. Dele-MIchael and her staff. I have dark skin and I wanted to address some longstanding skin issues. My previous dermatologist told me that there weren’t any treatments available because of my dark complexion. So I was relieved and excited when I discovered Dr. Dele-Michael and tbh, I am beyond happy with everything. She is great and you won’t regret the decision. The best african american dermatologist here in NYC!

I have been a patient of Dr. D. Michaels for almost four (4) years. I transition to NY from DMV area. While in MD I had several skin tags removed I was told that they woud not return.
Well they did. I was referred to Dr. Del Michaels by my Primary Care Dr to temove a sebaceous cyst from back.The skin tags were removed and has not returned.  The cyst was removed as well. Presently, I am having Chemical Peels and my face is "flawless."  The next procedure will be tighen my  skin on.my face. I have visited all 3 locations. My favorite is Washington Heights.
The staff is Awesome but my favorite is Ashley & Clinton. If you want a new you please call and make an appt. You will not be disappointed. Get that new you for 2021 and beyond.
